IMAPAccount tcs
# https://ews.tcsbank.ru/EWS/Exchange.asmx
Host imap.tcsbank.ru
User a.akselrod
PassCmd "cat ~/pass"
TLSType IMAPS
CertificateFile /opt/homebrew/Cellar/ca-certificates/2024-03-11/share/ca-certificates/cacert.pem
AuthMechs LOGIN
TLSVersions +1.2

IMAPStore tcs-remote
Account tcs

MaildirStore tcs-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path ~/.mail/tcs/
Inbox ~/.mail/tcs/Inbox

Channel tcs
Far :tcs-remote:
Near :tcs-local:
# Exclude everything under the internal [Gmail] folder, except the interesting folders
#Patterns *Â ![Goods]* "[Goods]/Sent Mail" "[Goods]/Starred" "[Goods]/All Mail"
# Or include everything
#Patterns *
# Automatically create missing mailboxes, both locally and on the server
Create Both
# Sync the movement of messages between folders and deletions, add after making sure the sync works
Expunge Both
# Save the synchronization state files in the relevant directory
SyncState *